{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c7b5ef8cad","title":"吴光清的档案材料与“‘一打三反’运动”","origin":"根据网络材料打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"46ddd0459e","index":0,"year":1971,"month":3,"day":23,"articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"}],"tags":[{"id":"2e99ca34d1","name":"一打三反","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0ea1dbba0a","type":"title","text":"吴光清的档案材料与“‘一打三反’运动”","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"9cf8b7126f","type":"subtitle","text":"第一份：（蓝油墨印制表格）","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"56fa7c9c09","type":"subtitle","text":"（甘肃永登县）红城公社宁朔大队“一打三反”运动中犯有错误人员登记表","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"4acd9c3659","type":"paragraph","text":"姓名吴光清，姓别男，年令（龄）45，族别汉，党员，个人出身农民，家庭成份贫，现任职务生产队长，住址，红城公社宁朔第四生产队。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"237e2f121d","type":"paragraph","text":"主要错误事实：","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"86059b7468","type":"paragraph","text":"一、69年贩卖自产清油14斤（折成本价10.64元，每斤0.76），对（兑）换小麦104斤，折现金14.04元，除成本，取利3.40元。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"59c8546f05","type":"paragraph","text":"二、67年打场时伙同别人每人偷分小麦35斤，68年种田时偷分小麦壹百零伍斤，以上共偷分生产队小麦140斤，折人民币18.90元正（整）。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"3f9e50f7a2","type":"paragraph","text":"在运动中的表现和退赔情况：交待问题老实，有悔改表现。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"69a5843e1f","type":"paragraph","text":"小队处理意见：偷分（小麦）如数追回，偷（投）机倒把补税，批评教育。宁（朔）四领（导）小组，71年4月3号。（小队长某某私印）","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"31df1102f7","type":"paragraph","text":"大队处理意见：偷分小麦全部退清，免交税款，大队处理。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"44f1e145cd","type":"paragraph","text":"公社处理意见：（空白）","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"fcee335927","type":"paragraph","text":" 1971年3月23日","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"c58a919e0c","type":"subtitle","text":"第二份：（手写）","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"40c1b874c8","type":"subtitle","text":"最高指示","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"02c3d5ecbc","type":"paragraph","text":"要斗私，批修","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"d9e8f08cba","type":"subtitle","text":"吴光清单行材料","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"67bb445ace","type":"paragraph","text":"吴光清，男，汉族，现年45岁，家庭成份贫农，个人出身农民，不识字。1955年参加中国共产党，系永登县红城公社宁朔第四队人。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"276fbf8bf0","type":"paragraph","text":"个人简历：解放前拉过长工，解放一贯务农，曾任生产队队长等职。","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"6635aa3d25","type":"paragraph","text":"主要问题：69年贩卖自产清油14斤（折成本价10.64元，每斤0.76元）兑换小麦104斤，折人民币14.04元，除成本，取利3.40元（见检字3号）。","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"21d750ec09","type":"paragraph","text":"67-68年伙同别人每人偷分生产队小麦共计140斤，折人民币18.90元。","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"fdb00da89b","type":"paragraph","text":"本人态度：吴光清做为一个共产党员，所犯的错误是严重的，但在“一打三反”运动中能认识问题、交待问题，有悔改的表现。","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"d020c08d60","type":"paragraph","text":"处理意见：根据本人的表现，经过广大贫下中农讨论，认识态度好，给予免税，偷盗私分粮食全部退清，经过大队党支部、革委会讨论，决定给予免交税款，贪污集体小麦全部退赔，并决定由大队革委会、党支部处理。","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"09268e1d24","type":"paragraph","text":" 永登县红城公社宁朔大队党支部、革委会1971年3月13日","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"9a47986d6b","type":"paragraph","text":"第三份：（手写）","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"b3ef1ad34e","type":"subtitle","text":"最高指示","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"71dbe3c8ed","type":"paragraph","text":"贪污和浪费是极大的犯罪","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"c65245e25b","type":"subtitle","text":"检讨书","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"32d7288a76","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席教导我们说：“见损害群众利益的行为不愤恨、不劝告、不制止、不解释，听之任之。”由于个人对毛主席著作学的不够，立场不稳，自己忘了是一个共产党 员，自己没有真正站在无产阶级和人民大众方面，没有用我们伟大领袖毛主席的教导要求自己因此，在一九六七和一九六九年偷分了队里的粮食。一九六七年在打场 的时候，偷分了五升。在一九六八年三月份在山里种田偷了105斤。毛主席说，“贪污和浪费是极大的犯罪”，经过这“一打两反”运动以后，对我有很大的教 育，使我深该（刻）的认识到自己作为一个共产党，但是做的一些事情是不符合人民利益的，今后一定要活学活用毛主席著作，高举毛泽东思想的伟大红旗，在工作 中一定要以共产党员的五个要求来对照自己的一言一行。","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"aa10a54c76","type":"paragraph","text":" 检讨人吴光清（私印）","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"67a03bbbbc","type":"paragraph","text":"1970年10月5日","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"0191e99911","type":"subtitle","text":"第四份：（手写）“谈字一号”","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"6aa198b226","type":"subtitle","text":"谈话记录","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"74ca61430a","type":"paragraph","text":"我在67年山里打场时，监印龙泽云在印印子的时候给我和达延科留下了一堆堆砂麦子，出售给王志忠。秤是达应科称的，我们每人（得）了钱，柒元左右，详数记不清楚，老达知道。","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"54e1865c53","type":"subtitle","text":"第五份：（手写）“谈字二号”","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"ae567cf15d","type":"subtitle","text":"谈话记录","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"0995d8a12d","type":"paragraph","text":"67年12月以后，在房家槽打场中，临走时，王企业提出没有多吃，我们每人五升分掉了，其中人有，龙泽云五升、王企业五升、吴广清五升、达延科五升、王有忠五升、赵应忠五升，我的是用了币7元，钱是龙泽云给的。","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"87d09bc366","type":"paragraph","text":"挥合（霍）浪费约三、四斗小麦，其中大部吃猪肉。清油4斤，喝酒2斤，参加人有：王育民、王延杰、王企成等人。","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"08b65aec96","type":"paragraph","text":"68年播种后，偷小麦每人1.5升，其中人，吴广清1.5升，赵应忠1.5升，王有忠1.5升，马安国1.5升，王作军1.5升，拿斗量给的。","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"be0628ff11","type":"paragraph","text":"在集体我做下了这一摊子事，请群众谅解。","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"e3bed99667","type":"paragraph","text":" 吴广清（红手印）70年7月6日","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"6325debb7b","type":"subtitle","text":"第六份：（手写）“谈字三号”","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"ed261652a7","type":"paragraph","text":"70年7月6号，宁朔队高家院","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"6d44319d8c","type":"paragraph","text":"吴光清谈自己投机倒把问题","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"bf9188862e","type":"paragraph","text":"69年3月份、5月份，自留地产的清油14斤，拿去房家槽子换了小麦104斤，自己吃掉了。","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"9ebddbb204","type":"paragraph","text":"记录人：（某某某）","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"49abd5aee2","type":"paragraph","text":" 被谈人：吴光清（红手印）70年7月6日","index":45,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"db97d7fd52","type":"subtitle","text":"第七份：（手写）“证字一号”","index":46,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"644890d450","type":"subtitle","text":"证明材料","index":47,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"4b7614ce58","type":"paragraph","text":"1967年11月份，我们在房家槽打场时，我们6人共偷小麦210斤，其中吴光清分小麦35斤。","index":48,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"},{"id":"cacbc82b26","type":"paragraph","text":" 证明人：达应科（红手印）1970年10月4日","index":49,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad"}],"page":{"id":"dabe554047","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c7b5ef8cad","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}